The Stuff in the Data layer 

    Cookie Functionality wont work if you have an ad/tracking blocker enabled
    Im using the word cookie because it reminds me of Cookie Monster and its more fun to say

    But Local Storage & Session Storage is much better. It is the same concept as cookies but is better (go-oogle it)




